    <table style="width: 100%;">
        <tr>
            <td align="left">To US CRE online Corp Admin,</td>
            <td align="right">@Model.Date.ToString("MMMM d, yyyy")</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <p><b style="color:darkgoldenrod">US CRE Online.com</b> Recorded Documents & Prelim Title Report Order:</p>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <td width="80"></td>
            <td>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Title Company:</td>
                        <td>@Model.TitleCompany</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Asset ID&#35;:</td>
                        <td>@Model.AssetId</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Property Address:</td>
                        <td>@Model.Address1 @Model.Address2, @Model.City, @Model.State @Model.Zip</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Property Type:</td>
                        <td>@Model.AssetDescription</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>APN:</td>
                        <td>@Model.APN</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Registrant &#40;<b>PI-B</b>&#41;:</td>
                        <td>@Model.Registrant</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <p>
        The above captioned <b>Principal Investor</b> &#123;&#34;<b><i>PI-B</i></b>&#34;&#125; has contracted &#40;e.g., &#34;Internet Portal &#38 Margin Disclosure Agreement&#34;&#41; with &#123;<b style="color:darkgoldenrod"><i>USCREonline.com LLC</i></b>&#125; 
        &#123;&#34;<b style="color:darkgoldenrod"><i>USC</i></b>&#34;&#125; as a registered prospective buyer of US CRE, and has formerly indicated vesting interest in the above captioned CRE Asset Data at <a href="http://www.uscreonline.com">www.USCREonline.com</a>.
        Per our relationship with @Model.TitleCompany, the <b>Preliminary Title Report</b> and <b>Recorded Documents</b> for the above captioned commercial investment property have been
        automatically ordered. 
    </p>
    <p>
        <b style="color:darkgoldenrod"><i>USC</i></b> will receive follow up notification when the <b>Recorded Documents</b>
        have been uploaded by @Model.TitleCompany to the above captioned Asset File. Per the terms and conditions of its Service Agreement with 
        <b style="color:darkgoldenrod"><i>USC</i></b>, @Model.TitleCompany will receive payment for its defined services according thereto.
    </p>
    <span>The Professional Staff</span><br />
    <span><b style="color:darkgoldenrod"><i>US CRE Online, LLC</i></b></span>
</body>
</html>